(935, 'ARCANE PRISM', 'Item', 'Item', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Position this prism in a location of your choosing and activate it. All allies within Close range of it gain a +1 bonus to their Spellcast Rolls. While activated, the prism can''t be moved. Once the prism is deactivated, it can''t be activated again until your next long rest.', 'https://daggerheartsrd.com/items/arcane-prism/'),
(936, 'ATTUNE RELIC', 'Item', 'Item', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'You gain a +1 bonus to your Instinct. You can only carry one relic.', 'https://daggerheartsrd.com/items/attune-relic/'),
(937, 'BAG OF FICKLESAND', 'Item', 'Item', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'You can convince this small bag of sand to be much heavier or lighter with a successful Presence Roll (10). Additionally, on a successful Finesse Roll (10), you can blow a bit of sand into a target''s face to make them temporarily Vulnerable.', 'https://daggerheartsrd.com/items/bag-of-ficklesand/'),
(938, 'BELT OF UNITY', 'Item', 'Item', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Once per session, you can spend 5 Hope to lead a Tag Team Roll with three PCs instead of two.', 'https://daggerheartsrd.com/items/belt-of-unity/'),
(939, 'BLOODSTONE', 'Item', 'Item', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'You can attach this stone to a weapon that doesn''t already have a feature. The weapon gains the following feature. Brutal: When you roll the maximum value on a damage die, roll an additional damage die.', 'https://daggerheartsrd.com/items/bloodstone/'),
(940, 'BOLSTER RELIC', 'Item', 'Item', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'You gain a +1 bonus to your Strength. You can only carry one relic.', 'https://daggerheartsrd.com/items/bolster-relic/'),
(941, 'BOX OF MANY GOODS', 'Item', 'Item', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Once per long rest, you can open this small box and roll a d12. On a result of 1-6, it''s empty. On a result of 7-10, it contains one random common consumable. On a result of 11-12, it contains two random common consumables.', 'https://daggerheartsrd.com/items/box-of-many-goods/'),
(942, 'CALMING PENDANT', 'Item', 'Item', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'When you would mark your last Stress, roll a d6. On a result of 5 or higher, don''t mark it.', 'https://daggerheartsrd.com/items/calming-pendant/'),
(943, 'CHARGING QUIVER', 'Item', 'Item', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'When you succeed on an attack with an arrow stored in this quiver, gain a bonus to the damage roll equal to your current tier.', 'https://daggerheartsrd.com/items/charging-quiver/'),
