(964, 'GREATSTONE', 'Item', 'Item', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'You can attach this stone to a weapon that doesn''t already have a feature. The weapon gains the following feature. Powerful: On a successful attack, roll an additional damage die and discard the lowest result.', 'https://daggerheartsrd.com/items/greatstone/'),
